- Heather Lad of Glencairn to you!

292
00:24:36.433 --> 00:24:38.727
OK, OK, OK.

293
00:24:38.894 --> 00:24:40.562
But remember this, Pigeon.

294
00:24:40.729 --> 00:24:44.316
