room for love and affection.

295
00:24:44.775 --> 00:24:46.986
When a baby moves in,

296
00:24:47.152 --> 00:24:49.738
the dog moves out.

297
00:24:56.036 --> 00:24:59.081
Let's see. that'll be about...

