301
00:25:15.139 --> 00:25:19.476
I'm afraid not.
Nobody ever knows for certain.

302
00:25:19.643 --> 00:25:22.312
All we can do is hope.

303
00:25:48.088 --> 00:25:51.800
Darling, are you sure
you want watermelon?

304
00:25:54.428 --> 00:25:56.013
And some chop suey too.

305
00:25:56.180 --> 00:25:58.724
Chop su...

