316
00:26:36.553 --> 00:26:38.138
Absolutely horrible.

317
00:26:38.305 --> 00:26:40.432
I never saw you look worse.

318
00:26:40.599 --> 00:26:45.187
Cheer up, Jim. Old Doc Jones
has never lost a father yet.

319
00:26:56.115 --> 00:26:57.991
Yes, Aunt Sarah, it's a boy.

320
00:26:58.700 --> 00:27:01.203
A boy. And... What's that?

321
00:27:01.995 --> 00:27:04.581
Eyes?
What colour are they?

322
00:27:04.748 --> 00:27:05.999
Well, oh, gosh.

323
00:27:06.166 --> 00:27:07.793
I forgot to look.

324
00:27:09.211 --> 00:27:12.172
A boy. It's a boy, it's a... Doctor!

325
00:27:13.173 --> 00:27:15.175
Doctor, it's a boy!

326
00:27:15.342 --> 00:27:17.302
Yes, yes, I know.

327
00:27:17.469 --> 00:27:18.595
A boy.

328
00:27:18.762 --> 00:27:20.097
Oh, boy, oh, boy!

329
00:27:20.264 --> 00:27:22.224
It's a boy, it's a boy, it's a boy!

330
00:27:22.391 --> 00:27:24.268
