00:28:13.275 --> 00:28:16.820
<i>It must be something grand</i>

339
00:28:18.071 --> 00:28:21.867
<i>'Cause everybody's smiling</i>

340
00:28:22.034 --> 00:28:26.455
<i>In a kind and wistful way</i>

341
00:28:26.622 --> 00:28:30.959
<i>And they haven't even noticed</i>

342
00:28:31.126 --> 00:28:34.880
<i>That I'm around today</i>

343
00:28:46.683 --> 00:28:49.061
<i>What is a baby, anyway?</i>

344
00:28:52.189 --> 00:28:54.983
<i>What is a baby?</i>

345
00:28:55.150 --> 00:28:57.819
<i>I must find out today</i>

346
00:28:57.986 --> 00:29:02.241
<i>What makes Jim Dear and Darling</i>

347
00:29:02.407 --> 00:29:08.247
<i>Act this way?</i>

