00:35:05.228 --> 00:35:07.731
Merciful heavens! My darlings.

412
00:35:07.897 --> 00:35:09.899
My precious pets.

413
00:35:11.651 --> 00:35:13.820
That wicked animal.

414
00:35:13.987 --> 00:35:18.658
Attacking my poor,
innocent little angels.

415
00:35:23.079 --> 00:35:24.456
Good afternoon, ma'am.

416
00:35:24.623 --> 00:35:26.416
What can I do for you?

417
00:35:26.583 --> 00:35:29.169
I want a muzzle.
A good, strong muzzle.

418
00:35:29.336 --> 00:35:31.838
Oh, yes, ma'am.
Now here's our latest.

419
00:35:32.005 --> 00:35:34.799
Combination leash and muzzle.

420
00:35:34.966 --> 00:35:37.010
Now, we'll just slip it on like this,

421
00:35:37.177 --> 00:35:38.595
and... No! No, no, no.

422
00:35:38.762 --> 00:35:41.056
Nice doggy. No, don't wiggle.

423
00:35:41.222 --> 00:35:43.600
Steady, now.
<i>Now...</i> Now, now.

424
00:35:43.767 --> 00:35:45.185
Careful, you little...

