00:35:45.352 --> 00:35:46.770
Watch out.

426
00:35:47.145 --> 00:35:49.648
- Careful, doggy.
- Come back!

427
00:35:49.814 --> 00:35:52.108
Get over here, I say.
Come back here.

428
00:37:28.913 --> 00:37:32.000
Hey, Pige, what are you doing
