00:37:36.337 --> 00:37:38.840
You poor kid.

432
00:37:39.007 --> 00:37:41.342
We've got to get this off.

433
00:37:42.552 --> 00:37:45.889
I think I know the very place.

434
00:37:46.055 --> 00:37:47.891
Come on.

435
00:37:51.144 --> 00:37:52.729
Well, here we are.

436
00:37:52.896 --> 00:37:55.523
