447
00:38:40.235 --> 00:38:43.571
- Were you addressing...?
- What's the matter? Can't you read?

448
00:38:43.738 --> 00:38:45.865
Why, yes, in several languages.

449
00:38:46.032 --> 00:38:48.368
Oh, a wise guy?

450
00:38:48.535 --> 00:38:52.372
All right, now, what's
this creature doing here?

451
00:38:52.539 --> 00:38:55.124
- He's not my dog.
- He's not?

452
00:38:55.291 --> 00:38:56.376
Go away. Get down.

453
00:38:56.543 --> 00:38:58.461
Go on. Why, certainly not, officer.

454
00:38:58.628 --> 00:39:00.505
I suppose you'll be tellin' me next

