00:39:14.644 --> 00:39:16.437
Trying to assassinate me, you are.

463
00:39:16.604 --> 00:39:18.398
Carrying concealed weapons.

464
00:39:26.531 --> 00:39:27.782
Come on, Pige.

465
00:39:27.949 --> 00:39:30.118
