00:40:16.247 --> 00:40:17.957
Timber!

478
00:40:18.124 --> 00:40:19.792
Pigeon, look out!

479
00:40:21.002 --> 00:40:23.004
Now what harebrained idiot would...

480
00:40:23.171 --> 00:40:25.381
