00:41:03.002 --> 00:41:04.462
Gotta get it moving.

495
00:41:04.629 --> 00:41:07.507
'Taint the cuttin' takes the time.

496
00:41:07.674 --> 00:41:10.218
It's the doggone haulin'.

497
00:41:11.844 --> 00:41:13.888
The haulin'. Exactly.

498
00:41:14.055 --> 00:41:17.433
- Now, what you need...
- I'd better bisect this section here.

499
00:41:17.600 --> 00:41:19.602
What you need is a log puller.

500
00:41:20.645 --> 00:41:23.523
I said a log puller!

501
00:41:25.108 --> 00:41:27.151
I ain't deaf, sonny.

502
00:41:27.318 --> 00:41:28.653
There's no need to...

503
00:41:28.820 --> 00:41:31.114
Did you say log puller?

504
00:41:31.280 --> 00:41:34.367
And by a lucky coincidence
you see before you,

505
00:41:34.534 --> 00:41:38.037
