509
00:41:45.628 --> 00:41:47.922
Guaranteed not to wear,
tear, rip or ravel.

510
00:41:48.089 --> 00:41:50.466
Show the customer the merchandise.

511
00:41:50.633 --> 00:41:53.886
And it cuts log-hauling time 66 percent.

512
00:41:54.679 --> 00:41:57.140
Sixty-six percent?

513
00:41:58.307 --> 00:41:59.559
Think of that.

514
00:41:59.726 --> 00:42:02.270
- Well, how's it work?
